    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are accepted at Gradation 1 per MRL 2 scoping. CFD predictions of NIH deviate from bench measurements by 8–21%, within the 25% acceptance criterion. The model is judged fit for the intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 criterion is satisfied at all five operating points.",
